PITTSBURGH, PA, January 3, 2017 – Matthews International Corporation (NASDAQ GSM: MATW; “Matthews” and/or the “Company”) today announced the completion of its purchase of A. + E. Ungricht GmbH + Co KG (hereafter “Ungricht”). Press Release




